title: Days of our Lives Thu, Jul 4, 2013
description:
Daniel's investigation could lead to Kristen's undoing.


Eric suffers a relapse and agrees to have blood-work done.


Jenn and JJ have another huge blowup after Jenn throws out JJ's new friend.


Gabi has a confession for Abby about her living situation.


Chad and Cameron agree to spend the holiday with Theo - together.


Nicole can't believe Sami has avoided jail time yet again.
